<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
{{>header title = "Service Invitation Created"}}

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">G</div>
                <div class="logo-text">GradPal</div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="header-title">Service Invitation Created</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello Team,
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                Great news! A new autonomous service invitation has been successfully created and is ready for
                distribution. This service will help enhance the learning experience for students.
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-title">{{serviceTitle}}</div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Created by:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">{{teacherName}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Subject:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">{{subject}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Status:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">Ready to Send</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What happens next:</h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>The invitation will be distributed to selected participants</li>
                    <li>Recipients will receive detailed service information</li>
                    <li>Service will activate once participants accept</li>
                    <li>You'll receive updates on invitation responses</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                This service is designed to provide personalized learning experiences and support educational goals.
                We're excited to see the positive impact it will have on the learning community.
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="#" class="cta-button">View Service Details</a>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                <strong>Need assistance?</strong><br>
                Our support team is here to help with any questions about the service setup or invitation process.
            </div>
        </div>
        {{> footer NationalPortal=NationalPortal}}
    </div>
</body>

</html>